      : 'You are a professional web content writer. Write a comprehensive, well-formatted article in English using HTML tags (h2, p, ul, li, strong). Write a strong introduction, then divide the content into sections with appropriate subheadings. Make it professional, engaging, and 100% original. Minimum 600 words.';
    var userMsg = keyword + (extraPrompt ? '\n\n' + extraPrompt : '');
